import React from "react";
import { Grid, Paper, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import { makeStyles } from "@material-ui/core/styles";

const CoeInfo = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container justifyContent="center">
      <Grid item>
        <Paper variant="outlined" square>
          <Grid container>
            <Grid item>
              <Typography>
                Cat A
                <Typography variant="span">
                  (CAR UP TO 1600CC & 97KW)
                </Typography>
              </Typography>
              <Typography>47,010</Typography>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item>
        <Paper variant="outlined" square>
          <Grid container>
            <Grid item>
              <Typography>
                Cat A
                <Typography variant="span">
                  (CAR UP TO 1600CC & 97KW)
                </Typography>
              </Typography>
              <Typography>47,010</Typography>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
};

export default CoeInfo;
